1
inspection shall be based on the fire codes in effect at the time of
1
2
the inspection and such vehicle shall remain in compliance with such
2
3
code for a period of ten (10) years. With the exception of an
3
4
automatic fire extinguishing system, such requirement shall apply to
4
5
vehicles including, but not limited to, vehicles utilizing electric
5
6
energy, liquefied petroleum gas, compressed natural gas, or a
6
7
